00:06:26.170 --> 00:06:29.628
And as you can see from
the heatmap that we did,

94
00:06:29.628 --> 00:06:33.806
the eye tracking heatmap that
uses a spotting content.

95
00:06:33.806 --> 00:06:38.710
That's how I would deal with
that particular objection.

96
00:06:38.710 --> 00:06:41.767
Another one is well,
it doesn't wow me, right?

97
00:06:41.767 --> 00:06:45.464
Well, it just doesn't wow me,
another one, right?

98
00:06:45.464 --> 00:06:50.356
Sometimes, my response to that is well,
it doesn't particularly wow me either, but

99
00:06:50.356 --> 00:06:52.760
we're not the target audience.

100
