Design tested well with our audience, and
I would advise against designing for us,

101
00:06:57.635 --> 00:07:00.531
rather than the people
we're trying to attract.

102
00:07:00.531 --> 00:07:03.723
So that's how I deal with that one and
again,

103
00:07:03.723 --> 00:07:08.933
I'll refer back to the semantic
differential survey where we said yeah,

104
00:07:08.933 --> 00:07:13.655
it ticks off all our keywords so
we know it appeals to our audience.

