00:07:13.655 --> 00:07:17.219
I vividly remember working on our
website back in the Myspace days,

106
00:07:17.219 --> 00:07:18.417
do you remember that?

107
00:07:18.417 --> 00:07:21.456
Yeah, probably not, you're all too young.

