00:08:12.280 --> 00:08:15.309
However, you might be
right in the real world,

123
00:08:15.309 --> 00:08:20.160
it might not, people might miss it,
so let's do some more testing.

124
00:08:20.160 --> 00:08:23.130
At which point they go we
don't have time for that,

