00:08:29.913 --> 00:08:34.468
gonna deal with this kind of stuff,
it makes an enormous difference.

128
00:08:34.468 --> 00:08:38.286
There's also another little factor
at play here and I can't remember,

129
00:08:38.286 --> 00:08:42.552
though I touched on this later, I might be
repeating myself but I will say it now.

130
00:08:42.552 --> 00:08:45.460
There's a psychological thing here,
all right?

