00:09:54.932 --> 00:09:56.501
you don't lose any face.

149
00:09:56.501 --> 00:09:57.705
Do you see what I mean?

150
00:09:57.705 --> 00:10:02.155
So you can basically preempt,
it's all very manipulative, isn't it?

