00:11:14.695 --> 00:11:17.988
produced, I can talk about how
it will improve engagement and

168
00:11:17.988 --> 00:11:22.780
lead generation because that's
the things marketing people care about.

169
00:11:22.780 --> 00:11:27.562
If I'm talking to a salesperson,
I can focus on lead quality and

170
00:11:27.562 --> 00:11:31.739
quantity so how many leads and
how good those leads are.

171
00:11:31.739 --> 00:11:36.843
If I'm talking to finance people,
I'll talk about how the improved

