00:11:45.850 --> 00:11:47.155
So it saves us money.

175
00:11:47.155 --> 00:11:49.664
And then if I'm talking to IT,

176
00:11:49.664 --> 00:11:55.365
I will emphasize how easy the site is
gonna be to build and to maintain.

177
00:11:55.365 --> 00:11:59.708
And actually, these are tips that work not
just for design, but tips that work with

178
00:11:59.708 --> 00:12:03.391
any, whenever you've got sell
something to somebody else, right?

179
00:12:03.391 --> 00:12:07.184
You appeal to their selfish gene, right?

