00:13:18.286 --> 00:13:26.246
It's I create a short video
presentation of the design, right?

199
00:13:26.246 --> 00:13:30.530
Why I've done it the way I've done it,
how I approached it,

200
00:13:30.530 --> 00:13:32.803
all the things that led up to it.

